WEBVTT

00:03:28.569 --> 00:03:31.242
jer u svojoj glavi vode rat

00:03:31.266 --> 00:03:32.809
koji nitko drugi ne vidi.

00:03:33.307 --> 00:03:34.529
S druge strane,

00:03:36.074 --> 00:03:39.057
velika većina ljudi gleda preko jaza

00:03:39.081 --> 00:03:40.232
i okreće glavom,

00:03:40.256 --> 00:03:43.272
kao, "Zašto moraš biti tako depresivan?"

00:03:44.817 --> 00:03:48.457
Možda prepoznate
takvu podjelu u svojem životu.

00:03:49.066 --> 00:03:51.055
Želite li sagraditi most preko nje?

00:03:51.712 --> 00:03:53.856
Možda ne želite sagraditi most,

00:03:53.880 --> 00:03:56.475
što je posve opravdan izbor.

00:03:57.182 --> 00:04:00.660
Ili biste htjeli izgraditi snažniju vezu,